reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 19, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Excellent purchase! Need to water them before use for get the full effect.
reviews.reviewText: I am replacing my original review of this item because they turned out to be excellent! I purchased these mostly for the aesthetics -for how they look- and not necessarily for the 'scent.' When I removed them from their box, I immediately noticed they were dry, cracking, flat, and had little scent. I let them sit out for a day and they remained the same, so I came here to review the item as being OK, but for whatever reason, I decided to wet the stems (since they are advertised as being used in the shower). This really made them flourish in how they look, feel, and smell! Super happy with my purchase!All I did was run them under some warm water and immediately the scent filled the room. They were not dry anymore and I was able to run my fingers up and down the stem to straighten out the leaf's and fluff them out. I placed them all over my home, mixing them in with other real and imitation plants. ^_^

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Soak prior to hanging
reviews.reviewText: These almost release too much fragrance. Presoaking made all the difference in their color vibrance and suppleness of the leaves. Aesthetically, I kind of wish I had ordered the larger bundle but the intensity of the fragrance from this smaller bundle is enough for my taste.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don’t waste your money
reviews.reviewText: I was optimistic when I bought this product because it was described as fresh. I thought it would be better and more fragrant than buying from a chain store where inventory might sit in a warehouse for months before hitting the shelves. I was wrong. When I opened the box there was very little scent and just about all of the leaves were flattened. I can only assume by looking at them that they’ve been processed for the essential oils already and what I bought was the leftover product after the branches were pressed and processed. Fantastic business move for the big business who extracts the eucalyptus oil but a crappy move on their part to sell their trash to unsuspecting consumers and advertise it as fresh and aromatic. I read reviews from others some good some not so good. One person suggested running them under water to hydrate the leaves. She thought it brought out the fragrance more and made the leaves appear fresh so I tried that. It did work to help bring life back to the leaves but didn’t do a thing as far as the scent. I’m pretty disappointed to have wasted money buying processed trash. Big business….. Do better for consumers

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I was hoping for fresh so the smell would fill my bathroom. No such luck. I have used it for day-core. It’s nice to look at.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very minimal fragrance- poorly scented.
reviews.reviewText: They look nice and appear to be good quality. However, there very minimal scent from this bushel. I hung them in the shower hoping the steam would enhance the fragrance. No luck. My husband couldn’t really smell much scent either. You have to put your face right up to it in order to smell the aroma. Disappointed.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 22, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Was super skeptical ordering these because of the mixed reviews. I was only ordering for the look, not the smell. I’m glad I took the chance because I’m happy with the way they look and they do smell faintly. I’m sure it won’t last long, but I love the way they look so I’m ok with that.I did soak them for a few minutes and then pulled them apart. I haven’t had any issues with the color running.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 2.0 out of 5 stars Not what I expected for a product that claims to be real eucalyptus
reviews.reviewText: After trying everything, reading the mixed reviews, and with my own experience I would have to say that I am disappointed with the order. When I opened the box, the eucalyptus smelled off but this was my first time ordering and even attempting to use eucalyptus in my shower. I place it on my shower head and there was no scent. I read in a couple reviews that I needed to soak it in cold water and that made the color run. Green coloring was coming out as I sprayed the eucalyptus with my shower head. I then tried using it while in the shower again and still no scent. I went really close to try and smell it but all I smelled was a weird chemical plastic smell. Sadly, I will be throwing all 3 bundles of eucalyptus away. The smell gave me a head ache.I gave it 2 stars because the eucalyptus is vey pretty and can be used for display purposes only.
